@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About — RigRoll</PageTitle>

<div class="about-container">
    <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
            <img src="images/RV-Checklist.jpg" alt="Cheerful cartoon RV at a lakeside campground" class="hero-image" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
            <i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i> About RigRoll
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-description">
            Your campground companion — because no one wants to realize
            the awning is still out when you're already on the highway. 🚐
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card what-card">
        <h2><i class="bi bi-signpost-split"></i> What Is RigRoll?</h2>
        <p>
            <strong>RigRoll</strong> is a collaborative, real-time checklist app
            built for RV campground setup and teardown. Everyone on your crew gets the same
            list on their phone — check items off together and watch progress update live.
            No more shouting across the campsite! 📋
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="bi bi-broadcast"></i>
            <h3>Real-Time Sync</h3>
            <p>Powered by SignalR — when someone checks an item, everyone sees it instantly. No refresh needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="bi bi-card-checklist"></i>
            <h3>Blueprints</h3>
            <p>Create reusable checklist blueprints for setup, teardown, or anything your crew needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="bi bi-people"></i>
            <h3>Crew Checklists</h3>
            <p>Activate a blueprint and everyone on the crew can pitch in. Teamwork makes the dream work — and keeps the slides from hitting that oak tree! 🤝</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="bi bi-phone"></i>
            <h3>Mobile-Friendly</h3>
            <p>Designed phone-first. Check off tasks with one thumb while holding a leveling block in the other.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card tech-card">
        <h2><i class="bi bi-gear"></i> Under the Hood</h2>
        <p>
            Built with modern tools so you can focus on camping, not troubleshooting:
        </p>
        <ul class="tech-list">
            <li><i class="bi bi-code-slash"></i> <strong>.NET 10</strong> &amp; <strong>Blazor Server</strong></li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-broadcast"></i> <strong>SignalR</strong> for real-time updates</li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-database"></i> <strong>Azure SQL</strong> for reliable data storage</li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-cloud"></i> Hosted on <strong>Azure</strong> with CI/CD via GitHub Actions</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card camp-card">
        <h2><i class="bi bi-emoji-smile"></i> Happy RigRolling!</h2>
        <p>
            Whether you're a weekend warrior or a full-timer, RigRoll keeps your
            crew organized so you can spend less time stressing and more time around the
            campfire. 🏕️🔥
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
